{"tid":736880,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[估省份] [威過城大]小學落成一年　兩層高球館樓頂塌陷","createTime":"2018-07-10T14:30:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-10T16:00:56.000Z","uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5d44faf86315680ca493792b129973a37a18ce5b","tid":736880,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T14:30:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180710/s00004/1531213035252\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180710%2Fs00004%2F1531213035252&d=eR1TBwj6C9DhNxCubXnTRttKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=4298f870\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180710%2Fs00004%2F1531213035252&h=a80a9899\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180710/s00004/1531213035252</a><br />\n<br />\n廣西欽州市一間小學的兩層高樓房，其鋼結構樓頂周日（8日）出現嚴重變形及塌陷，由於正值假日，事發時沒有師生在大樓中，故未造成傷亡。然而，該小學在去年9月才招生，有市民質疑是否牽涉質量問題。當地教育部門已派人到場調查，在現場加設圍欄，以防有人再受傷。<br />\n<br />\n涉事的欽州市第三十九小學於2016年開始興建，去年7月竣工，同年9月招生，現有逾1000名學生。樓頂幾乎完全倒塌的樓房為該校球館，鋼結構向內傾造成嚴重變形，但當地天氣近日未見有暴風雨，不少市民懷疑存有質量問題。該市有關部門正調查事故原因，將根據調查結果追究相關法律責任。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180710/s00004/21e6a585fb985a2b416ad4413bd206d6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180710%2Fs00004%2F21e6a585fb985a2b416ad4413bd206d6.jpg&h=eb79f57f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180710/s00004/21e55b330f7eeb8f4051d9dc95cb6de9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180710%2Fs00004%2F21e55b330f7eeb8f4051d9dc95cb6de9.jpg&h=80b067db&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b3ffc64459e4b405c13e44261a732436f11f3439","tid":736880,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T14:42:20.000Z","msg":"班死閪仔識唔閪識起樓架"},{"pid":"53cf3b2f20349a2be5ff300898bead25be565b0f","tid":736880,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T16:00:56.000Z","msg":"過兩年沙中線都係咁咋"}]}